  "description": "Maximum density, maximum decay, minimum damping. The marble monolith rings indefinitely — cold, dense, unyielding. A single note fills the room with inharmonic partials that sustain for 15 seconds. Slow LFO on brightness creates glacial timbral movement. The 2001 monolith, humming.",
